Definition
----------

The abstract definition of the

> A *ring* $$(R,+,*)$$ is a set $$R$$ together with two binary 
> operations $$+$$ and $$*$$ satisfying the following axioms
>
> 1. $$(R, +)$$ is an abelian group
> 2. $$(R, *)$$ is a monoid
> 3. Addition and multiplication satisfy the distributive law

Although 